            >
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
              Modern Wayland Desktop
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-6">
              Beautiful <span class="text-pink">and Fast</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-subtext0 mb-8 text-lg">
              Hyprland compositor with buttery smooth animations, rounded
              corners, and blur effects. A desktop that's a joy to use.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="glass-card rounded-xl p-4 hover-lift">
                <div class="text-2xl mb-2"></div>
                <div class="text-text font-semibold">60fps Animations</div>
